data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3-bed, 2-bath brick ranch offers a blend of comfort and durability. With a brand new roof, HVAC and most appliances less than 7 years old, this property ensures worry-free living. The finished basement, heated/cooled garage, and workshop provide extra space for your needs. Enjoy the fenced backyard for privacy. The primary bedroom even has it's own private yard! The home is designed with handicap accessibility in mind, featuring zero-entry into the home, no-curb shower, and accessible vanity in the primary bathroom. This property is ready for your personal touch to make it uniquely yours. With a little love, this house can become your perfect home, tailored to your style and preferences. Don't miss the chance to create lasting memories in this inviting space.
